            <ChoiceText>Queen Procipinee joins you at the massive stone doors to the forge.

"The spells are unlike anything I've seen.  They don't block us from entering the forge as much as they remove whatever is beyond those walls from this world.  I cannot guess at what lies beyond.  I believe I can open the way, though it will require all of my effort to do so.  Be careful, for if you fail we will not be able to try it again."

With great effort Procipinee channels her power towards the forge.  It has remained closed since the titan that her kingdom is named for came through.  The doors do not open, they are not real doors, they simply shimmer like starlight through clouds.</ChoiceText>
