	<QuestDef InternalName="Quest_FrogAltar">
        <DisplayName>Frog Altar</DisplayName>
        <Description>There is a forgotten altar here, a symbol to ancient gods and a time when men were ruled by superstition and fear.  You scoffed at these cults once, but after seeing the tragedy and dark power in the east, you wonder if there may be more to these myths.</Description>
        <IsStartingPointQuest>0</IsStartingPointQuest>
        <ShortTextAccept>I should investigate these myths</ShortTextAccept>
        <ShortTextDeny>I have no time for superstitions</ShortTextDeny>
        <RewardText>Unknown</RewardText>
